title: Exploring the Capabilities of ChatGPT
eventShortDescription:
​April .NET User Group: Exploring the Capabilities of ChatGPT 

Get ready to explore the future of AI with GPT-4, the upcoming AI powerhouse, with Calum Simpson! 🧠🤖

SSW Solution Architect Calum will showcase GPT-4's cutting-edge capabilities with real-world demos, offering practical insights and ideas to inspire innovation in your software development projects. 👨‍💻

Discover how GPT-4 can revolutionize your workflow, and increase your productivity and efficiency. This is your chance to gain insight into the future of AI and software development. Get ready to learn and explore the exciting possibilities of GPT-4! 🤘

--

Join us in person from 6 pm in Sydney, Melbourne, or Brisbane:

SSW Sydney – Live 🔴
SSW Melbourne – Watch party 🎦
SSW Brisbane – Watch party 🎦
